originalText.text: The buses are in hideous and unsafe conditions.  The chairs and floor is dirty, the outside of the bus needs a good cleaning and possible a paint job. One time the bus was on the highway and the front doors opened up.  The driver closed the doorz and quickly went on his way.  They sometimes leave late and the bus is always overcrowded.  I'd rather pay the extra 30 or 40 dollars and take a flight for comfort and quick transportation.  I will never take the bus again.
